OL,3,C'Business is booming': Scottish kilt
OL,4,Cmakers discuss soaring sales ahead of
OL,5,CEuros
OL,7,FITV News Scotland Reporter Louise
OL,8,FScott heard from one kilt maker who
OL,9,Fhas experienced a 'big few weeks' of
OL,10,Fbusiness ahead of Euro 2024
OL,12,FWhen you think about the build-up to
OL,13,FScotland going to the Euros, one thing
OL,14,Fyou might not have thought about is
OL,15,Fkilts.
OL,17,FYes, that's right - kilts.
OL,19,FThe item of clothing is a crucial part
OL,20,Fof the packing list for any Tartan
OL,21,FArmy supporter.
