OL,7,FKilts, of course, come in many
OL,8,Fdifferent tartans, whether it's
OL,9,Ffamilies or clans.
OL,11,FWe're hoping Scotland get off to a
OL,12,Fwinning start against tournament hosts
OL,13,FGermany on Friday, but already off to
OL,14,Fa flying start are the kilt makers
OL,15,Facross Scotland.
OL,17,FEwan MacDonald, a kilt maker from
OL,18,FPaisley, explained to ITV News that
OL,19,F"business has been booming", ahead of
OL,20,Fthe Euros getting underway
