OL,3,C'Business is booming': Scottish kilt
OL,4,Cmakers discuss soaring sales ahead of
OL,5,CEuros
OL,7,FHe said: "We've been really busy end
OL,8,Fof May, but all of June has been
OL,9,Freally busy.
OL,11,F"So, buying kilts, if they (customers)
OL,12,Fcan't find a kilt they're hiring it,
OL,13,Fthey're repairing old kilts, they're
OL,14,Fgetting sporrans (and) accessories.
OL,15,FSo, it's been a big last few weeks."
OL,17,FHe added: "You have a ten times better
OL,18,Ftime if you're wearing a kilt, so they
OL,19,Fjust want to be part of the Tartan
OL,20,FArmy basically."
