OL,7,FIf you're in the market for a kilt
OL,8,Fjust be aware that costings can extend
OL,9,Finto the hundreds of pounds, even for
OL,10,Fa pre-owned, former hire kilt.
OL,12,FBrand new kilts, depending on the
OL,13,Fcloth that it's made of and how the
OL,14,Fcustomer wants it to be made, can push
OL,15,Fthe price to between #500-900,
OL,16,Faccording to Mr MacDonald.
